title: CLEAR_VEHICLE_XENON_LIGHTS_CUSTOM_COLOR
content:
0x2867ED8C// ClearVehicleXenonLightsCustomColor
void CLEAR_VEHICLE_XENON_LIGHTS_CUSTOM_COLOR(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle handle.Removes vehicle xenon lights custom RGB color.
codeBlocks:
local ped = PlayerPedId()
local vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsIn(ped, false)
-- Example usage for CLEAR_VEHICLE_XENON_LIGHTS_CUSTOM_COLOR
ClearVehicleXenonLightsCustomColor(vehicle)
